
================
Node intilization
================
mkdir node-app
cd node-app
code .
npm init
npm i express
node index.js
live serve extion   : npm i nodemon --save-dev
npm run start       :  node index.js 
npm run start-dev   :  nodemon index.js


======
Docker
======
build dokcer file and name the image        : docker build -t express-node-app .
get all images                              : docker image ls

run continer with new name                  :  docker run --name express-node-app-conatiner express-node-app  
port forward without showing extra terminal : docker run --name express-node-app-conatiner -d -p 3000:3000 express-node-app  

delete container                            : docker rm express-node-app-conatiner -f
show all containers                         : docker ps